    "The impact of increasing shots on LLM varies across different tasks.",
    "The influence of increasing shot quantities on LLM is task-dependent.",
    "Increasing shots for relatively simple tasks like SC does not noticeably improve performance.",
    "Additionally, for datasets like MR and Twitter, as well as stance and comparison tasks, performance even deteriorates with the increase in shots.",
    "It could be due to handling more extended contexts misleading LLM's results."
